-Configuration de la connection : 
    - mettre en Internet Protocol Version 4 (TCP/IPv4)
    - mettre IP adresse pour le port Ethernet : 192.168.1.XXX
    - subnet masque : 255.255.255.0
    - Gateway et DNS pas n√©cessaire
-Configuration sur terminal :
    nmtui
-Error ARP request "Who have IP"
    -Configure NM IP at this IP


-LiDAR 1 connection setup
    sudo nmcli connection add con-name lidar_1 ifname enxf8e43b6cecab type ethernet
    sudo nmcli connection modify lidar_1 ipv4.addresses 192.168.1.221/24 ipv4.method manual ipv6.method disabled
    sudo nmcli connection up lidar_1

-LiDAR 2 connection setup
    sudo nmcli connection add con-name lidar_2 ifname enxf8e43b6cecab type ethernet
    sudo nmcli connection modify lidar_2 ipv4.addresses 192.168.1.222/24 ipv4.method manual ipv6.method disabled
    sudo nmcli connection up lidar_2


